chia.app_readme:
Chia

This container runs as root user.

When a port is set to < 9000. Host Networking is enabled automatically.

Also NodePort services turn to ClusterIP services, to avoid attempts to bind ports twice.

Key file is stored in /plots/keyfile and is generated automatically, only if the file does not exist. If you want to use your own keyfile, you can create a file called keyfile in the /plots directory and it will be used instead.

When set on harvester mode keys variable is set to none and no generation is performed.
chia.description: Chia is a modern cryptocurrency built from scratch, designed to be efficient, decentralized, and secure.
chia.name: chia
chia.title: Chia
